---

<BaseLayout title={`About | ${company.name}`}>
  <main>
    <PageHero
      eyebrow="About us"
      title="Dry-type Bushing Manufacturer | 550kV Testing Capability"
      text="Founded 2013, 50,000+ installations, ISO-certified factory with in-house 550kV EHV testing laboratory. Co-drafter of DL/T 1001-2024."
      image="/assets/factory-testing-line.jpg"
    />

    <section class="trust-row" aria-label="Factory trust numbers">
      {trustStats.map((item) => (
        <article>
          <div>
            <strong>{item.value}</strong>
            <p>{item.label}</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </section>

    <section class="section split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Company profile</p>
        <h2>National high-tech enterprise specializing in RIP/RIF dry-type capacitive bushings</h2>
        <p>
          {company.name} was founded in 2013 in Gaomi City, Shandong Province. As a national
          high-tech enterprise integrating R&amp;D, production and sales, we are committed to providing
          high-quality, safe and environmentally friendly dry-type capacitive bushing solutions for the
          global power and energy industry.
        </p>
        <p>
          We manufacture Resin Impregnated Paper (RIP) and Resin Impregnated Fiber (RIF) bushings
          covering Oil-Air, Oil-SF6, Oil-Oil, High-Current, GIS and Wall Bushing types.
          With over 50,000 bushings delivered, including 4,917 units for railway projects holding
          75% of China's railway market share, our products serve State Grid, China Southern Power
          Grid, and major energy groups across 60+ export countries.
        </p>
        <p>
          As co-drafter of the DL/T 1001-2024 power industry standard, Qixing combines manufacturing
          expertise with standards-level technical knowledge. Every bushing is type-tested in our
          in-house 550kV EHV laboratory and shipped with full inspection documentation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-panel">
        <h3>Factory highlights</h3>
        <dl>
          {factoryHighlights.map((item) => (
            <div>
              <dt>{item.dt}</dt>
              <dd>{item.dd}</dd>
            </div>
          ))}
        </dl>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section split about-product-section">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">RIP Bushing</p>
        <h2>Resin Impregnated Paper insulation for transformer and GIS interfaces</h2>
        <p>
          RIP bushings use resin-impregnated paper as the main insulation system, giving stable
          electrical performance, compact dimensions, lighter weight and maintenance-free operation
          for high-voltage transmission and transformation equipment.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-media-grid">
        {aboutMedia.rip.map((src, index) => (
          <figure>
            <img src={src} alt={`RIP dry-type bushing product ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section split about-product-section alt">
      <div class="about-media-grid">
        {aboutMedia.rif.map((src, index) => (
          <figure>
            <img src={src} alt={`RIF dry-type bushing product ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">RIF Bushing</p>
        <h2>Resin Impregnated Fiber structure for lightweight, flexible installation</h2>
        <p>
          RIF bushings use fiberglass as the main insulation material with resin impregnation,
          supporting oil-free design, maintenance-free operation, any-angle installation and stable
          electrical performance without combustion or explosion risk.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section dark-section">
      <div class="section-heading compact">
        <p class="eyebrow">Testing &amp; manufacturing</p>
        <h2>550kV EHV testing laboratory with fully shielded design</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="split dark-split">
        <div class="about-media-grid lab-gallery">
          {aboutMedia.lab.map((src, index) => (
            <figure>
              <img src={src} alt={`550kV EHV laboratory view ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
            </figure>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="light-text">
            Our in-house 550kV extra-high-voltage testing laboratory features a fully shielded
            hexahedral design with partial discharge background levels below 3pC, ensuring
            every bushing undergoes rigorous type-test verification before delivery.
            The facility is equipped for power frequency, lightning impulse and partial discharge
            testing up to the highest voltage classes we manufacture.
          </p>
          <ul class="check-list light">
            {labEquipment.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Certifications &amp; honors</p>
        <h2>ISO certified, IEC &amp; GB/T compliant</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-media-grid certificate-gallery">
        {aboutMedia.certifications.map((src, index) => (
          <figure>
            <img src={src} alt={`Qixing certification and honor ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="badge-row">
        {certifications.map((item) => <span>{item}</span>)}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Key projects</p>
        <h2>Proven in railways, substations and energy infrastructure</h2>
        <p>
          Products are widely used in key railway, grid and energy projects including
          Lhasa-Nyingchi Railway, Chengdu-Chongqing High-Speed Railway, Changsha-Kunming
          High-Speed Railway, Zhengzhou-Fuyang Railway and utility-scale solar projects.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-media-grid project-gallery">
        {aboutMedia.projects.map((src, index) => (
          <figure>
            <img src={src} alt={`Qixing reference project site ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Major customers</p>
        <h2>Trusted by industry leaders</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="customer-row">
        {customers.map((item) => <span>{item}</span>)}
      </div>
      <div class="client-logo-marquee about-client-marquee" aria-label="Major customer logos">
        {customerLogoRows.map((row, rowIndex) => (
          <div class="client-row">
            <div class={`client-track ${rowIndex === 1 ? "reverse" : ""}`}>
              {[...row, ...row].map((src, index) => (
                <div class="client-logo-card">
                  <img src={src} alt={`Major customer logo ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Global reach</p>
        <h2>Trusted by power grids, railways and energy projects in 60+ countries</h2>
        <p>
          From the China-Laos Railway and Lhasa-Nyingchi high-altitude line to State Grid 500kV
          substations and utility-scale solar projects, Qixing bushings are proven in demanding
          environments. Our products also serve Huadian, Huaneng, SPIC, CHN Energy,
          Datang and other major energy groups.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-grid media-cases">
        {applications.map((item) => (
          <article>
            <img src={item.image} alt={`${item.title} application`} loading="lazy" />
            <h3>{item.title}</h3>
            <p>{item.text}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section split about-product-section">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Future vision</p>
        <h2>Building a world-class brand in power insulation</h2>
        <p>
          Looking ahead, Qixing will continue to focus on dry-type capacitive bushing technology,
          high-voltage insulation engineering and international project support, creating lasting
          value for global customers and contributing to a stable, sustainable energy future.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-media-grid future-gallery">
        {aboutMedia.future.map((src, index) => (
          <figure>
            <img src={src} alt={`Qixing factory panorama ${index + 1}`} loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-panel">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Engineering support</p>
        <h2>Talk to Mark Yan about your project requirements</h2>
        <p>Send your voltage, current and application - get a technical recommendation within 24 hours.</p>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-avatar" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 12.5a4.5 4.5 0 1 0 0-9 4.5 4.5 0 0 0 0 9Zm0 2c-4.4 0-8 2.4-8 5.3 0 .7.5 1.2 1.2 1.2h13.6c.7 0 1.2-.5 1.2-1.2 0-2.9-3.6-5.3-8-5.3Z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>{company.contact.person}</strong>
            <span>{company.contact.title}</span>
            <a href={company.contact.whatsappUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener">{company.contact.phone} (WhatsApp)</a>
            <a href={`mailto:${company.contact.email}`}>{company.contact.email}</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="button primary orange" href="/contact/">Contact Mark Yan →</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
